metadata.name: Label Scout #1
metadata.description:
Label Scout for Probably A Label.

Probably A Label is a web3 record label founded by Probably Nothing, a web3 company, and Warner Records, a web2 company. Our goal is to create a more engaging connection between music consumers, artists and label resources.

The PAL Pass is a collection of 5,555 NFT passes that give holders access to the Probably A Label music ecosystem.
